Articles.Content: I am using realism overhaul, and I was forced to remove procedural parts in order to get my game to launch. Whenever I try to launch any vehicle, there simply will be no stage for my engine, therefore pressing space does nothing at all (except maybe deploy parachutes or decouple some nodes).

Log file?

It's player.log if you're on a Mac, or output.log.txt if you're on Windows.
Here's my entire log folder, incase you need more https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0B4pIAi8-DxTCdFJEMHJWOGNVLVE
It's high security. Too high security.
